WHY AGPL?
=========
This project links to the Swiss Ephemeris library (sweph), which is itself
distributed under AGPL-3.0. AGPL requires that any software that uses Swiss
Ephemeris and is made available over a network (e.g., as a web API) must also
be released under AGPL or a compatible license, with full source code
available to all users of the network service.

Astrodienst AG also offers a commercial license for Swiss Ephemeris that
removes this requirement. If you wish to use this code in a closed-source
network service, you must:

  1. Obtain a commercial Swiss Ephemeris license from Astrodienst AG, AND
  2. Replace AGPL components of this project with your own implementation, OR
     fork and re-license under terms compatible with your commercial license.

For details on the Swiss Ephemeris licensing model, see:
  https://www.astro.com/swisseph/swephinfo_e.htm
